# Gen-AI Components:

## Encoding:
 is the process of transforming raw input — text, images, audio — into a numerical representation the model can work with. Think of it as translating human-readable data into a language math understands.

## Embedding:
 is the process of transforming raw input — text, images, audio — into a numerical representation the model can work with. Think of it as translating human-readable data into a language math understands.

