#### To Create **venv** use below command
```
 python -m venv env
 ```
 
 ###E to activate env, use below command
 ```
 env\Scripts\activate  
 ```
 pip install requests==2.0
 
 #### to get all python's are in machine, use below command

 ```
 uv python list
 ```
 #### to use particular python version during virtual environment, use below command

uv python install <give the specific version of the python>

use only cpython interpreter.
 ```
 uv venv env --python cpython-3.11.14-windows-x86_64-none
 ```
 #### to install all the libraries from requirements.txt file, use below command

 ```
 uv pip install -r requirements.txt
 ```

